Summerset Isles

Altmer

Illustration of an Altmer male

Summary:

  • Homeland of the High Elves/Altmer.

  • The province is a collection of islands southwest of mainland Tamriel.

  • The largest island is Summerset itself, while the second largest is Auridon, which is east of Summerset and acts as a buffer to mainland Tamriel.

  • The Summerset Isles are a place of breathtaking beauty, a paradisiacal region of crystal-clear waters, towering spires, and ancient, elegant architecture.

  • Contains the capital of the Aldmeri Dominion, Alinor.

Real-world counterpart/inspiration:

Originally just the stereotypical Tolkien/D&D High Elves, the closest real-world inspiration would be Imperial China.
